  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Shitty little comic panel style (Picture security breach endings) cutscene
    would occur after the incredibly well animted belt explosion.


    X gets a
    glimpse into multiple outcomes of how his future as a hero could turn out. One
    where he stands on the ruins of the city, in front of the Heroes Guild which
    has now caught flame. Another where he sits from atop the guild''s watchtower,
    justice league type shit.


    Then the cutscene ends and X awakens at the guild
    hall. Belt on, and confused how he got from point A to B. Just a fuzzy feeling,
    like he sleptwalked there.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2180264, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
